name: pair-project-101
description: 1. Buatlah public/private repository baru 2. Centang initialize readme option   	![new-repository](assets/new-repository.png) 3. Buat branch baru bernama `development` dari branch `master` / `main`   	![development-branch](assets/development-branch.png) 4. Buka settings - branches dan ubah default branch menjadi `development`   	![default-branch](assets/default-branch.png) 5. Buka settings - manage access dan invite teman pair dan instruktur   	![invite](assets/invite.png) 6. Clone repository, inisialisasi project structure & file minimum untuk memulai project, kemudian push ke `development`   	![initial](assets/initial.png)
